====Pokémon Adventures====
{{main|Whitley (Adventures)}}
Whitley from [[Pokémon Adventures]] is modeled after Rosa. She first appeared near the end of the {{MangaArc|Black & White}} as a {{tc|Team Plasma Grunt}}, and later served as one of the main characters of the {{MangaArc|Black 2 & White 2}}. She is a supporter of {{adv|N}}'s philosophies and has a timid personality.
